ction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":72,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBQQ040EGAUiEwiDyIH3t-uTAxUSg7oAHTryKydIuMTXvYfWjIP0AcoBBLqiWjg=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbVJPVFB4b2hRaXFOT19NZlVtY2NXWnkzRS00QXxBQ3Jtc0ttS2pvZEY3Tk9ha2FGWU5WalItV0c0LUgxVFdXVTlMbnRzNTVFRjczUWkzNkFVRkkwWURWNDJqUFl1MVpqQnAtLWxpa01KMGc1TUtSYmtFX0hncmxzR29lNlFwNXBNbzF1X0NJU2JETzNVRjQ5RC1Eaw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=9AYysHe14jg","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbVJPVFB4b2hRaXFOT19NZlVtY2NXWnkzRS00QXxBQ3Jtc0ttS2pvZEY3Tk9ha2FGWU5WalItV0c0LUgxVFdXVTlMbnRzNTVFRjczUWkzNkFVRkkwWURWNDJqUFl1MVpqQnAtLWxpa01KMGc1TUtSYmtFX0hncmxzR29lNlFwNXBNbzF1X0NJU2JETzNVRjQ5RC1Eaw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=9AYysHe14jg","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":184,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBQQ040EGAUiEwiDyIH3t-uTAxUSg7oAHTryKydIuMTXvYfWjIP0AcoBBLqiWjg=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbTJyNmMtUVpNalVjcjZJdkZYeWNmVm85N3Vhd3xBQ3Jtc0ttQ0g5aUVxV1pRanliTjZPdHFiZDQ3VnluZHJMVzJGV1NhUm5nRFNURnVEWGxGNUJhZzRYQkp4U3g1Slp0VmFzMTQ0UjVHSDVzdEdEQ28yNDFHeGJUZTNFLVAzaWNLM0lzZnQ4dmd2blBsTkhDVXhTaw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paypal.com%2Fcgi-bin%2Fwebscr%3Fcmd%3D_s-xclick